WEBVTT

00:00:00.199 --> 00:00:04.500
Good morning, family. How are y'all doing today? Well, praise the Lord!

00:00:04.501 --> 00:00:10.119
I'm excited to be here today. I have some things on my heart we're going to pray about.

00:00:10.120 --> 00:00:19.396
You know, a lot of people—I guess I caused some confusion on not the last video, but the video before—people are asking, "What are you talking about, the economy?

00:00:19.397 --> 00:00:34.756
I thought it was going to crash and all this stuff."I saw when President Trump wins the election, the economy and the news of winning causes a ripple throughout the whole world.

00:00:34.757 --> 00:00:40.521
There are a lot of people that will be excited; yes, there will be a lot of people that are not excited.

00:00:40.522 --> 00:00:51.964
But for the most part, what I was shown was that there is an economic—like people, when they hear the news, the stock market rallies and gets excited and things happen.

00:00:51.965 --> 00:01:00.029
I saw a pumping of the economy. And so people were like, "I thought you said you saw the economy crash?"I did, and I still do.

00:01:00.030 --> 00:01:09.698
I told you all that it was like a house of cards. I saw the BRICS nations rising up and trying to create their digital platform.

00:01:09.699 --> 00:01:28.272
I said, "I believe this is me looking into a vision."Whenever I've said this, there is depth perception in a vision where you are looking, whether it's a year, a month, or two years or whatever; it's very hard to tell.

00:01:28.273 --> 00:01:34.758
You have to... it's like this: the Lord told me, "You are going to have to be so precise.

00:01:34.759 --> 00:01:46.319
It's going to be like a ticking of a clock when it comes to investments."He said because if you're too early, you're too early; if you're too late, you're too late.

00:01:46.320 --> 00:01:51.333
You have to be just like a clock. He was referring in my heart because my favorite watch is a Rolex.

00:01:51.334 --> 00:02:03.078
I've never owned one, but I think they're beautiful. And he talked to me about how precise a tick is: tick, tick, tick, tick, tick.

00:02:03.079 --> 00:02:13.638
Invest. Tick, tick, tick. Don't invest. If you do it by the precision of the heartbeat of the Father, you will not miss it.

00:02:13.639 --> 00:02:18.175
But if you're doing it too early, it is too early in investments.

00:02:18.176 --> 00:02:32.274
If you get in there and you invest too early and he's not saying that yet, and you put something into something, then you could lose money, right?

00:02:32.275 --> 00:02:42.938
Or it could be way too early or whatever. And then all of a sudden he says, "Invest in this,"and you are scared to invest in it because your flesh is involved.

00:02:42.939 --> 00:02:50.916
And he's saying, "Do something,"and you're going, "Man, I don't know."And then it shoots up really high and you miss the opportunity to put your money in it.

00:02:50.917 --> 00:03:01.885
And so that's why I'm saying it has to be you, when you are doing stuff with money, hearing his voice right on every single thing.

00:03:01.886 --> 00:03:29.556
So whenever I tell you the Lord is telling me a season of grace, a time of grace, he said, "Brandon, there has been much prayer that has gone before me over the month of October, and I am granting more grace over what I would see was going to be hell on earth."There was like a small little window.

00:03:29.557 --> 00:03:34.922
Now, what that entails—if that's until the first of the year, a small window—I have no idea.

00:03:34.923 --> 00:03:40.654
Ladies and gentlemen, I'm human, and when I'm praying, I'm just telling you exactly what I'm seeing.

00:03:40.655 --> 00:03:50.976
And so I want you to pray about it too. It's not for you to ride on the back and just go, "Hey, you figure it out, Brother Brandon."No, no, no.

00:03:50.977 --> 00:03:58.679
You help me. If I bring something to you to pray about and it doesn't witness with you, then say, "That doesn't sound like anything.

00:03:58.680 --> 00:04:04.972
That doesn't witness with my spirit at all. I don't believe you're hearing the Lord."That's fine.

00:04:04.973 --> 00:04:09.455
We hear in part and we see in part. And so what I may see, you may not see.

00:04:09.456 --> 00:04:20.374
You know, a lot of people were like, "What did you pray about the New York Yankees and all that for so long?"I brought it up because the Lord brought it up to me.

00:04:20.375 --> 00:04:30.267
I saw the vision of the New York Yankees going to the World Series and the Los Angeles Dodgers clear back in like May.

00:04:30.268 --> 00:04:38.638
And I saw attempted attacks on Yankee Stadium, and he kept telling me, "Watch the Yankees.

00:04:38.639 --> 00:04:52.438
Watch the Yankees."That's the only word he was giving me: "Watch and pray for the Yankees."And so when you add to or take away from anything whenever he's talking to you... I'm just giving you what I'm learning.

00:04:52.439 --> 00:05:08.512
I'm thinking in my natural mind, even into August, and he says, "Pay attention to the Yankees."I'm thinking, "Wow, the Yankees are going to go to the World Series and win it."But he said it would be the Los Angeles Dodgers and the Yankees.

00:05:08.513 --> 00:05:25.318
So just like he said, it happened. So I'm at October, and I told the pastor, "Hey, I believe the Yankees are going to win,"because we just talk sports. And so I'm seeing this at the prayer conference.

00:05:25.319 --> 00:05:41.971
Whenever I'm talking about this to the pastor, I'm going, "Well, you know, the Lord's been telling me to watch the Yankees since May."I mean, this is a long time—that we pray over it, that there would be no attacks at the World Series, because I knew they were going to the World Series.

00:05:41.972 --> 00:05:47.848
I just had no idea if they were going to win. I saw them going, but then I saw Los Angeles.

00:05:47.849 --> 00:06:07.433
So when it got to the Friday when they started the game, the Lord says, "Los Angeles will win it in game five, the whole thing."And I thought, "Game five, the whole thing?"But they'll have three games to pray over at Yankee Stadium that nothing happens.

00:06:07.434 --> 00:06:21.359
And that was, I believe, Monday, Tuesday, Wednesday. Three games in a row at Yankee Stadium, but they would lose in game five.

00:06:21.360 --> 00:06:25.495
And I was like, "Oh, wow."Lord, I thought they were going to win.

00:06:25.496 --> 00:06:39.620
Not that it matters, but it's learning to listen to his voice. Do not assume anything.

00:06:39.621 --> 00:06:51.127
Do not think for him, thinking, "Well, I believe this is what you're saying."Don't add to it. He said, "Pray for the Yankees. Pray for the stadium.

00:06:51.128 --> 00:07:05.473
Pray for this."And here I am, you start adding to the prophetic word by saying, "Oh, the Yankees are going to win."But when it got down to teaching me...

00:07:05.474 --> 00:07:11.781
I'm just letting you all in on something that I never let a lot of people in on, and I'm obviously going to let thousands in now.

00:07:11.782 --> 00:07:20.638
But this is how I learn, and this is how he teaches me to flow in my gift and how I see and hear.

00:07:20.639 --> 00:07:24.999
Because I'm a work in progress and I'm hearing things, this is how I do it.

00:07:25.000 --> 00:07:34.031
And so whenever the Lord is instructing me, you get pieces of the puzzle and you build yourself.

00:07:34.032 --> 00:07:40.363
You do not become a champion in anything without practice. I don't care who you are.

00:07:40.364 --> 00:07:52.813
If you think that you're just going to jump right out and be a LeBron James or a Michael Jordan in anything you do, it's impossible. You have to learn how to...

00:07:52.814 --> 00:08:13.727
when you're riding a bike, you learn just as much how to pick yourself up when you fall than you do whenever you are an amazing BMX biker, or a Joe Montana, or Troy Aikman, or Emmitt Smith, or somebody in sports that was the best at their level.

00:08:13.728 --> 00:08:23.342
You do not become a great until you practice in high school all the way up to college, and then you keep going.

00:08:23.343 --> 00:08:31.724
You do not become a great overnight, basically, in anything.

00:08:31.725 --> 00:08:37.073
And even listening to the voice of the Lord, you practice his presence.

00:08:37.074 --> 00:08:47.513
You practice, and when you fall, you pick yourself back up. You keep going and you go, "Well, man, I missed it big,"whatever.

00:08:47.514 --> 00:08:54.521
I'm trying to paint a picture for you all. So here, I saw about the Yankees.

00:08:54.522 --> 00:09:04.078
So I'm assuming privately between my wife and I and my kids and my pastor that the Yankees were going to win.

00:09:04.079 --> 00:09:07.853
And this is just something that we just talked about privately. I never made it public.

00:09:07.854 --> 00:09:14.161
I just talked about this because I thought, "Man, the Yankees are going to win. This is cool."And we'll watch it play out.

00:09:14.162 --> 00:09:31.434
So when it got down to that Friday when the World Series started, the Lord came to me and he said, "Brandon, Los Angeles will win it in game five."And I said, "Wow."I said, "The Yankees are only going to win one game?"So you just talk over things with the Lord.

00:09:31.435 --> 00:09:38.837
I just make a note of it. I tell my son. We archive it so we know, because this is me learning.

00:09:38.838 --> 00:09:47.601
And so it gets down to game five and the Yankees are up by like six points or whatever it was. It was a lot.

00:09:47.602 --> 00:09:56.968
And I thought, "Man, I've missed it."And then all of a sudden, in the fifth inning, they started falling apart.

00:09:56.969 --> 00:10:05.479
And they blew a humongous lead with errors and dropping the ball and throwing the ball.

00:10:05.480 --> 00:10:13.190
It was just stupid plays. And they lost the lead in the fifth inning in game five.

00:10:13.191 --> 00:10:25.516
And so for you that don't care about sports, I'm just trying to... for people who want to learn.

00:10:25.517 --> 00:10:36.327
So it got down to game five and they blew the lead, and they lost the game. And it was just like the Lord said.

00:10:36.327 --> 00:10:41.319
But at the point whenever I'm looking into it in the natural, I'm thinking, "Man, I missed it.

00:10:41.320 --> 00:10:54.915
There's going to be a game six."And I told my wife, "Surely I didn't miss both what the Lord said about the fifth game and who was going to win."Because I assumed it was going to be the Yankees, like I said.

00:10:54.916 --> 00:11:08.108
And lo and behold, it happened just like the Lord said. And then he scolded me and he said, "Brandon, you can never think for me that this is what you're assuming that I'm saying.

00:11:08.109 --> 00:11:23.108
Never add to a word that I'm giving you."This was a good example of what I'm trying to practice with you, trying for you to learn that whenever you are looking into a vision, you do not add to or take away from anything.

00:11:23.109 --> 00:11:28.241
He said, "Pray for the Yankees in the stadium."It's exactly what he said.

00:11:28.242 --> 00:11:39.924
And he said, "I told you Los Angeles."He said, "I never told you anything else about who would win."I said, "You're right."I just assumed because you kept telling me to watch the Yankees.

00:11:39.925 --> 00:11:56.425
And I learned something. Even at the level I am and what I'm hearing and seeing, I still have correction from the Father all the time telling me, "Brandon, you're off.

00:11:56.426 --> 00:12:07.057
You need to learn and you need to grow."So you may say, "Brandon, you have it all together,"and there's a lot of you that don't think I have it all together because I get the comments.

00:12:07.058 --> 00:12:14.198
But there's a lot of people that do and they put you on a pedestal. And I'm telling you, I'm a work in progress just like you.

00:12:14.199 --> 00:12:20.233
And yes, some people are further along in their walk with the Lord than others, but it just all takes a day-to-day.

00:12:20.234 --> 00:12:27.025
We all learn by trial and error. We all learn just like by riding a bike how to listen to him.

00:12:27.026 --> 00:12:39.056
And my thing is sports. We talk about sports all the time. We talk about who's going to win the NBA championships. We talk about the Super Bowl.

00:12:39.057 --> 00:12:52.098
He'll tell me way in advance who's going to win the Super Bowl, and I'll write it down and I'll keep it private between me and my kids and my wife. It's something I learned how to build off of.

00:12:52.099 --> 00:13:06.741
And even being so precise of something that I saw clear back in May—which is very hard to do in the natural—I still missed it in my heart and I walked away discouraged.

00:13:06.742 --> 00:13:18.098
I thought, "Well..."and I'm just being real with y'all. I think it's good to be real, not to be so hyper...

00:13:18.099 --> 00:13:33.170
I'm just real. So going back to what I saw about the economy. And so you say, "Well, you said the economy is going to crash.

00:13:33.171 --> 00:13:41.293
You said that the interest rates were going to be lowered in April and you missed it."And I apologize; I told you all I did.

00:13:41.294 --> 00:13:54.025
I saw what I assumed was the deflating of the balloon. I saw the deflating of the balloon and I added to it, saying that the interest rates were going to come down.

00:13:54.026 --> 00:13:57.977
I saw numbers and I thought the interest rates were coming down. I missed it.

00:13:57.978 --> 00:14:10.957
Then I saw the summer months and I saw the housing market shaking. I saw the thin membrane shaking, shaking, shaking.

00:14:10.957 --> 00:14:15.799
Nothing happened for the interest rates until, I believe, it was September.

00:14:15.800 --> 00:14:25.085
And then I told you all that I saw the bubble pop in October, and there would be an event happen in October.

00:14:25.086 --> 00:14:32.599
So then the Lord says to me, "You're going to pray over the economy."We're praying for 30 days.

00:14:32.600 --> 00:14:35.898
And he said, "Much prayer in Washington, all these places...

00:14:35.899 --> 00:14:54.094
prayer has gone up before my throne."And now, I saw this: going into 2025, that there would be great economic distress, a dam breaking, all the stuff flowing behind the dam.

00:14:54.095 --> 00:15:02.601
And I still see it. I believe in my spirit... I'm going to tell you...

00:15:02.602 --> 00:15:04.485
because you're going to say, "I don't really care what you think.

00:15:04.486 --> 00:15:09.046
What does the Lord say?"This is how I do it. If you want to listen to the channel, fine.

00:15:09.047 --> 00:15:15.215
If you don't, go listen to somebody else, and that's fine. I'm not trying to sway you or twist your arm to be here.

00:15:15.216 --> 00:15:22.974
Thank you for being here. If you want to pray with me, fine. But this is what I see.

00:15:22.975 --> 00:15:42.923
Okay, so adding to and taking away from anything when you see...

00:15:42.924 --> 00:15:53.192
so here we are in October. Did we see any kind of big bubble bust? He said it was a mark in the spirit realm about October.

00:15:53.193 --> 00:16:01.559
And everybody says, "There's an October surprise."I never heard the word "October surprise."I never prophesied one time on my channel that there would be an October surprise.

00:16:01.560 --> 00:16:06.697
I said there would be an event that happens in October that would cause the economy to shake.

00:16:06.698 --> 00:16:15.646
The BRICS nations met and they had the major event around the 21st to the 24th.

00:16:15.647 --> 00:16:41.597
And so I believed in my spirit that that was the event because every single time I've seen and I've prayed, it's been around the BRICS creating, with China, Russia, Iran, Saudi Arabia, the petrodollar, all that stuff, creating their own currency, creating their own digital platform against the dollar, causing the dollar to crumble.

00:16:41.598 --> 00:16:54.397
That's what I've seen. And I've seen it completely destroy the dollar with having Saudi Arabia and the petrodollar joining up with China and all this other stuff.

00:16:54.398 --> 00:17:01.803
So when that happens, I still believe it because the Lord told me a house of cards will fall.

00:17:01.804 --> 00:17:07.703
And I saw the house of cards falling, and I saw a major shaking still taking place.

00:17:07.704 --> 00:17:17.966
And I saw the 1920s and 1930s and a major stock market crash similar to what happened. And then I saw the four oak trees.

00:17:17.967 --> 00:17:37.036
The Lord told me to pray about the four oak trees standing strong in this economic decision that will be made, which I believe is four years of President Trump's presidency—one, two, three, four years over the United States economy.

00:17:37.037 --> 00:17:47.119
So when you're seeing about the economy escalating and getting better for a small little window...

00:17:47.120 --> 00:17:56.203
what is it? A week, two weeks? I don't know. I'm learning to not try to say "this is what I feel."No, this is what I saw.

00:17:56.204 --> 00:18:01.219
He did not give me a direct time frame yet. So I saw the economy...

00:18:01.220 --> 00:18:06.681
it could be just one day, it could be two days, it could be a week. Who knows?

00:18:06.682 --> 00:18:13.150
All I know is I saw the economy taking off for maybe a 24-hour window. I don't know.

00:18:13.151 --> 00:18:19.257
Because they announce that he wins, and then I saw Jerome Powell again.

00:18:19.258 --> 00:18:25.367
So Jerome Powell was still running things. And so I saw the house of cards fall.

00:18:25.368 --> 00:18:34.036
I saw the economy fall. Whether or not that is in January, I still saw the dam bursting.

00:18:34.037 --> 00:18:39.742
I still saw the terrible times ahead for the United States, a humbling coming.

00:18:39.743 --> 00:18:48.023
And people say, "What is the falling like gnats?"I saw the plague and I've warned you all about this plague.

00:18:48.024 --> 00:18:56.694
Donald Trump was president when the plague is released and he announces that he's shutting down air travel.

00:18:56.695 --> 00:19:04.968
And I saw a massive plague coming again that was worse than COVID on steroids.

00:19:04.969 --> 00:19:11.236
It was huge. From what I saw, 350 plus million people will perish.

00:19:11.237 --> 00:19:17.647
And I saw over 30 million in the United States of America. And it was very, very bad.

00:19:17.648 --> 00:19:22.123
And I saw people again, the Lord showed me, falling like gnats.

00:19:22.124 --> 00:19:29.145
And people around you that you thought were really, really strong Christians, and people that were walking a compromise.

00:19:29.146 --> 00:19:35.565
And that's why I preached such a strong word yesterday telling you all not to ride the fence.

00:19:35.566 --> 00:19:39.646
If you're all in, you're all in, but do not play Christianity right now.

00:19:39.647 --> 00:19:45.744
And people got really upset at me. I got the emails. They think, "Well, you're being judgmental.

00:19:45.745 --> 00:19:51.071
You need to just pray and shut up."All the things that you all said in the emails—crazy.

00:19:51.072 --> 00:19:58.079
And I'm like, "No, I'm going to say what the Holy Spirit tells me to say."And if you don't like it, go click somebody else's video.

00:19:58.080 --> 00:20:06.390
And that's just how bold it is. You're not going to come on here with a spirit of intimidation and demonic spirits of Jezebel and try to knock me down.

00:20:06.391 --> 00:20:11.590
I'm not listening to you. I'm going to be even more bold about it because I know I touched a nerve.

00:20:11.591 --> 00:20:19.153
And if you don't like it, like I said, bye-bye. I don't care. I'm going to tell what the Holy Spirit tells me to say.

00:20:19.154 --> 00:20:24.574
And so we are in that time frame that you have to get your boats ready.

00:20:24.575 --> 00:20:27.558
I've heard Liberty Ministries talk about getting your boats ready.

00:20:27.559 --> 00:20:32.194
I'm talking about, folks, you've got to be ready for what's coming.

00:20:32.195 --> 00:20:36.145
And you say, "Well, is it delayed?"I don't know time frames, folks.

00:20:36.146 --> 00:20:44.346
All I do is I see what I see and I do it with all I have. I listen and I pray and I seek him with all I have.

00:20:44.347 --> 00:20:53.809
You do the same and he'll speak to you. I'm nothing more than just another person that God uses.

00:20:53.810 --> 00:21:03.083
He'll use you. He'll use everybody out there. If you yield yourself to him, he will show you things to come.

00:21:03.084 --> 00:21:11.392
I'm anointed and appointed for such a time as this, obviously, to do this. So we're going to pray over what I've seen.

00:21:11.393 --> 00:21:23.344
And so I know I've made a long video here that probably is just redundant, but I want to make it clear because obviously you all think I cause a lot of confusion.

00:21:23.345 --> 00:21:33.653
A lot of y'all did. And when I say a lot, you know, a couple hundred out of how many thousands. But you want to clear it up for the couple hundred.

00:21:33.654 --> 00:21:40.549
Well, we're going to take communion together today and we're going to pray and we're going to seek him.

00:21:40.550 --> 00:21:53.694
And I believe with all my heart the best is yet to come. He said he gave us an extended period of time of grace, that he's not coming back yet.

00:21:53.695 --> 00:22:01.272
He said he wants the harvest. Most people get upset because they're ready for Jesus to come back, but we occupy until he comes.

00:22:01.273 --> 00:22:10.864
And most people are ready to abandon ship, but we have to fight until we get the harvest that he's wanting.

00:22:10.865 --> 00:22:20.801
Or we're not going to go... do what you're supposed to do. Fight with all your heart, with all your mind, all your soul, all your strength.

00:22:20.802 --> 00:22:26.075
Love him. Fight for him in the spirit realm and pray for the unsaved loved ones.

00:22:26.076 --> 00:22:29.365
He doesn't want anyone to perish, but all to come to repentance.

00:22:29.366 --> 00:22:35.276
Especially the ones that he knows are about ready to step over and get born again and saved.

00:22:35.277 --> 00:22:56.827
If it was you and you were riding the fence of Christianity, wouldn't you want them to fight just a little bit more?

00:22:56.828 --> 00:23:07.887
If you were really close... we get frustrated with his decisions because we want to go home, and I get that.

00:23:07.888 --> 00:23:23.520
But the Lord told me, he said, "If you're satisfied with your life and you're elderly, you can be promoted."You don't want to die because you're scared of death, a lot of you, but the Lord wants to promote you if you're ready to be promoted and you say, "Hey, I'm satisfied.

00:23:23.521 --> 00:23:38.399
Go home then."But the young ones have to get this job done. And if it was you that was riding the fence and you were backsliding and you weren't right with the Lord and you never accepted him, wouldn't you want somebody to give you a little bit more time?

00:23:38.400 --> 00:23:49.446
Maybe you say, "Well, I'm saved."Well, no, but there's somebody out there that's praying for somebody that's just that close to giving their heart to Jesus Christ.

00:23:49.447 --> 00:23:59.823
And the Lord sees it, and he wants that person. He'll go after the one and leave the ninety-nine.

00:23:59.824 --> 00:24:07.399
Folks, I believe with all my heart there's the one out there today. There's somebody out there that would be just that close.

00:24:07.400 --> 00:24:17.729
You're watching this video and you have been challenged and you're saying, "Man, Brandon, I want to come to Jesus. I don't really know how. I've been a big bad sinner.

00:24:17.730 --> 00:24:31.456
I've done all these bad things and there's no way that the Lord would forgive me."But I want to tell you this: it doesn't matter how big of a sinner you think you are, Jesus Christ forgave you of all those sins.

00:24:31.457 --> 00:24:43.105
If you ask him to, he'll wash you and cleanse you like a big sponge bath. He'll just wash you down and clean you up and get you right.

00:24:43.106 --> 00:24:49.242
Put a new robe on you, get you a clean gown of salvation, and get you a mansion in heaven.

00:24:49.243 --> 00:24:59.158
Start building it, doing everything they can to get everything ready for you because you're his child.

00:24:59.159 --> 00:25:06.718
You don't realize how much the Lord loves you. He loves you so much and you've been running and running and running.

00:25:06.719 --> 00:25:13.659
You say, "Well, I'll be a Christian whenever I get all this other stuff done,"because sin is fun for a season, ladies and gentlemen.

00:25:13.660 --> 00:25:31.816
And you think, "Well, I'll just go out and party and sew my wild oats,"and then you get to the end of your life and you think, "Well, I can't serve him now because I've been bad all my life."So there's never a win situation in sin.

00:25:31.817 --> 00:25:40.861
You never win because you're always going to talk yourself out of it because you think, "Now I'm really unworthy."But you never were worthy.

00:25:40.861 --> 00:25:44.026
Nobody was. It was all by grace you were saved through faith.

00:25:44.027 --> 00:25:53.063
So why do you keep running from the Father whenever he's waiting there with his arms wide open?

00:25:53.064 --> 00:26:05.908
He is the best thing that's ever happened to me. There's nothing the world had to offer in sin to make me want to stay in the sin.

